Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:43.33,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然认真但又笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.61,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}相互碰撞的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:48.28,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使如此  我也想拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:50.44,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}巨大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:55.04,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就在这里  从此起步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.98,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我明白的  不净是快乐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:00.91,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这是在考验我们吧  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:03.95,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因为  这份痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:05.89,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}会让我们通往未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:09.85,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大家齐心协力能让自己变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:11.10,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:14.58,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不断的变化  We'll be star!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:19.62,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果能为自己所喜欢的事加油的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:24.41,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那就以新目的地为目标吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:29.42,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果能坚信自己所喜欢的事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:34.29,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那就怀揣这份雀跃感前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:37.38,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}舍弃胆小的坏习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:39.81,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用那份灿烂的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:42.22,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飞翔  飞翔  朝着更高的目标
