Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:34.41,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要大家期望  那就能够做到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:37.37,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}比谁都要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.41,0:22:41.46,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀揣满腔的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:46.67,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}以那凉风习习的大道为目标
