Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.44,0:00:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上集的LOVELIVE！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以组成了偶像团体为起点的我们三人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝试挑战了出道演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缪斯的出道演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望演唱会能够成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  希望能大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样我们也要歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着能在全场观众面前高唱的一天前进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳你以后想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳想当偶像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像？真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞蹈的动作一定都记住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这里请小泉来读一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大声点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was be preferable by the…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才这里开始  今井你读下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}He gave me some…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话根本不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟最近每天都要来看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似突然对它着迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们发传单去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一会会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有五人不被承认是社团的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法参加像样的社团活动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脖子上毛茸茸的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟  这样做不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就先用弓来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀  都怪你说了奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许被讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们只是在开心地和你玩罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没水了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是负责养羊驼的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是饲养员所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是来看演唱会的花阳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑过来看的一年生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成为偶像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果  太直接啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太耀眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕  不会让你受委屈的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉看着像个坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不适当强硬一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西木野同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你能再说一遍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得西木野同学很适合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌也唱的非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜欢她的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就去把她劝诱过来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她说绝对不要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我又说错话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快点体育课要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天说了今天要决定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不决定的话  大家都要开始活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那个  凛你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田径部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田径吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想进偶像部试试？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？那种事…才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的  花阳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谎的时候一定会勾着手指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会跟你一起去的  走吧  去学姐那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？真的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成为偶像什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳你这么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会出名的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是等一下  等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…能让我任性的说两句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我说要成为偶像的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不适合当偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我那么男孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发也这么短
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想想以前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱  凛你超适合穿裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一直穿裤子的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你有裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比谁先跑到校门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是先换一件再来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不适合当偶像什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西木野同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生完全没聚集过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得偶像活动对音木坂学院来说有弊无利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为学校的状况就限制学生的活动有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  为了让学校继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请你让学生会独立活动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  看上去也不是一点人气都没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是之前的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是谁拍了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:09:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我是和真姬同学同班的小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在在医院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家经营着医院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后准备让她继承下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了高中以后还没有一个朋友来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还很担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  你掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是西木野同学的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为  为什么你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了缪斯的海报了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗  我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认错人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  学生手册也掉在那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  都怪你说了奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我成为校园偶像？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放学时一直在音乐室那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听西木野同学的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢到想一直听下去  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学已经决定要进医学部了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说我的音乐已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我  你才想当偶像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之前的演唱会你不是看的很入迷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来西木野同学也去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我只是正好路过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做就去做不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  我也会为你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有各种各样的苦衷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给妈妈买点点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOVELIVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要看店  你在上面等一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能到这个程度的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没关系  我们才该说对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没想到海未居然会在练习姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都  都怪穗乃果去看店人不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你真的要来做偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是偶然过来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就请她吃点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗村特产穗村馒头  简称穗馒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果  我带电脑来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  我的老是在关键时候坏掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  找到影片了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没确认  估计是在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁拍的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播放数好多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么多人在看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段表演得很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里练习了很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功的时候差点想握拳大叫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  花阳  你那边很难看清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要认真考虑下来做校园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是很适合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实也不喜欢在人前表演
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得自己不适合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有时候也会忘词  运动神经也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很冒失的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是职业的偶像  我们肯定瞬间就不及格了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果是校园偶像的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀着一份干劲和热忱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以试着去做好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那就是校园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  如果你想做的话  就试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  练习可是很严格的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好考虑一下  再告诉我们答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们随时都在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那让身影朦胧的雾霭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}在这里也完全地消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的话  就试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}好  到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从远方的山上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这篇文章中与四郎的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究  究竟是什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  下面是…佐藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这篇文章中与四郎的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西木野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的声音其实是很好听的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有放大声音好好练习而已了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大声点  站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西木野同学？为什么你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在鼓励我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要去学姐那里说想做偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好别那么催促她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她再有点自信也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么西木野同学要来管凛和花阳的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想说  要唱的话  那样做会比较好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳总是优柔寡断的  干脆点决定会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  昨天和她交谈后我觉得好像不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  不要吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳走吧  学姐她们要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一定要去的话  就我带她去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于音乐我给的建议会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缪斯的歌也是我作曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  如果要带的话  就让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来带她去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人  来人救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  你想要加入我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  花阳很早以前就想当偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子唱歌挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是字面上的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你要犹豫到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是去做会比较好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的话  就试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我也说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发出声音是很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的  你一直以来  都想成为偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛  西木野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  我会一直支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也说过会稍微为你加油的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫小泉花阳  一年级  人也很矮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音又小  又怕生  没有任何特长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  可是我想做偶像的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  请让我加入缪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳  太了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  西木野同学也在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁哭了啊  我才没有哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  你们两个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个打算怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  什么怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还在召集成员哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晨练每天都要那么早起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你的眼镜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我换隐形眼镜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  很可爱  非常可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西木野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你不带眼镜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便直接叫我名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会直呼你们的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真姬真姬真姬真姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真姬真姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞了害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真姬好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}（要谈偶像还早10年！）
